import {
  Routes,
  Route,
  BrowserRouter as Router
} from "react-router-dom"
import Home from "./routes/Home"
import Navbar from "./components/Navbar"
function App() {
  return (
    <Router>
      <Navbar />
      <Routes>
        <Route path="/" exact element={<Home />} />
        <Route
          path="/edit/:id"
          exact
          element={<EditExercise />}
        />
        <Route
          path="/create"
          exact
          element={<CreateExercise />}
        />
        <Route
          path="/user"
          exact
          element={<CreateUser />}
        />
      </Routes>
    </Router>
  )
}

export default App
